title: Ceph Storage: Status
agents: linux
catalog: os/storage
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
  This check monitors the status of a Ceph cluster by evaluating its health, OSD map, and PG map.

  The check reports on various metrics, including overall health, OSD full status, placement groups, and recovering bytes per second.

item:
  The literal string "Status".

discovery:
  The check will discover a single service.

cluster:
 On a cluster only the first nodes' response is checked.
